4 vijayet nṛśaṃsyatā yā me bahiḥ prāvartayati
5 sundarāt paśuśālāyāḥ yasminn aham aśayiṣam meṣaḥ,
6 vṛkānām śatrur ye yuddhanti tasmin;

7 anyena vācānena, anyena ca romaṇā,
8 punar āgacchāmi kaviḥ, ca tataḥ mūle
9 mama snānasya gṛhṇāmi śiroveṣṭanam;

13 Tataś caikas tejomayaḥ puruṣaḥ asmābhiḥ abhimukham ājagāma
14 tasmād viśeṣād yasmad ādyam
15 yasya pratinidhayaḥ Khristena niyuktaḥ āsīt;

19 Yathā kadācid dīrghagrīvaḥ
20 sakhīṃ prati sthitaḥ, anyonyam
21 parivartataḥ kuvit kuvit kuvantau sneham;

70 Anekebhyaḥ nakṣatrebhyaḥ ayam prakāśaḥ mama āgacchati;
71 Api tu saḥ mama hṛdaye pūrva eva tam asāvayat,
72 Yaḥ parama netā parama gāyakaḥ āsīt.

91 Īśāyaḥ āha yad ekāikā vastrāṇi dhārayanti
92 sva-deśe tad-dviguṇāni bhavanti:
93 tatas tasya deśaḥ ayam madhuraḥ saṁsāraḥ;

97 Evaṃ ca, eṣām vacanām anta-samaye prathamam,
98 "Sperent in te" iti asmābhiḥ ūrdhvam śrutam;
99 yatra sarvāṇi maṇḍalāni pratyuttaram adaduḥ.

109 Aham tatra kāṇe evaṃ cakre ca sthitaḥ abhavam;
110 Mama patnī ca tatra dṛṣṭim adadhāt,
111 Yathā tu vadhūr mūkaḥ aniṣṭhā ca.

118 Yaḥ kaścid adhyavasāyaṃ kṛtvā prayatate
119 sūryagrahaṇamaṇḍalamalpamapi draṣṭum,
120 sa draṣṭukāmaḥ adarśanaṃ prāpnoti;

127 Dve stole saha subhe klaustre
128 Dve jyotishi ekāki ye āruhur;
129 Evaṃ ca tvam ānayasi tava jagati."
